Credits - Firefly Contributors Credits
======================================

This project aims to create a simple way to follow contributions
on git based projects.

It should be use as an internal web view.

You can see an example of the project running at:

    http://credits.sahid.us

Please, feel free to push Pull Request on the branch credits.sahid.us to
add new Open Source project.

This was largely inspired by:
  http://www.spinics.net/lists/ceph-devel/msg18941.html
